# Character Abilities
ABILITY:FEAT|TYPE:NORMAL|CATEGORY:FEAT|KEY:Eschew Materials|TYPE:General|DESC:You can cast any spell that has a material component costing 1 gp or less without needing that component.
ABILITY:FEAT|TYPE:NORMAL|CATEGORY:FEAT|KEY:Combat Casting|TYPE:General.EpicWizard.CosmicDescryer|DESC:You get a +4 bonus on Concentration checks made to cast a spell or use a spell-like ability while on the defensive or while you are grappling or pinned.
ABILITY:FEAT|TYPE:NORMAL|CATEGORY:FEAT|KEY:Improved Initiative|TYPE:General.Fighter|DESC:You get a +4 bonus on initiative checks.
ABILITY:FEAT|TYPE:NORMAL|CATEGORY:FEAT|KEY:Spell Penetration|TYPE:General.EpicWizard.CosmicDescryer|DESC:You get a +2 bonus on caster level checks (1d20 + caster level) made to overcome a creature's spell resistance.
ABILITY:FEAT|TYPE:NORMAL|CATEGORY:FEAT|KEY:Craft Wand|TYPE:ItemCreation.Wizard|DESC:You can create a wand of any 4th-level or lower spell that you know.
ABILITY:FEAT|TYPE:NORMAL|CATEGORY:FEAT|KEY:Craft Staff|TYPE:ItemCreation.Wizard|DESC:You can create any staff whose prerequisites you meet.
ABILITY:FEAT|TYPE:NORMAL|CATEGORY:FEAT|KEY:Brew Potion|TYPE:ItemCreation.Wizard|DESC:You can create a potion of any 3rd-level or lower spell that you know and that targets one or more creatures.
ABILITY:FEAT|TYPE:NORMAL|CATEGORY:FEAT|KEY:Forge Ring|TYPE:ItemCreation.Wizard|DESC:You can create any ring whose prerequisites you meet.
