ABILITY:Animal Trick|TYPE:NORMAL|CATEGORY:Special Ability|KEY:Animal Trick ~ Come|TYPE:AnimalTrick|DESC:The animal comes to you, even if it normally would not do so.
ABILITY:Animal Trick|TYPE:NORMAL|CATEGORY:Special Ability|KEY:Animal Trick ~ Defend|TYPE:AnimalTrick|DESC:The animal defends you (or is ready to defend you if no threat is present), even without any command being given. Alternatively, you can command the animal to defend another specific character.
ABILITY:Animal Trick|TYPE:NORMAL|CATEGORY:Special Ability|KEY:Animal Trick ~ Attack|TYPE:AnimalTrick|DESC:The animal attacks apparent enemies.|DESC:Animal will attack all creatures&pipe;PREABILITY&colon;1,CATEGORY=Animal Trick,Animal Trick ~ Attack II
ABILITY:Animal Trick|TYPE:NORMAL|CATEGORY:Special Ability|KEY:Animal Trick ~ Fetch|TYPE:AnimalTrick|DESC:The animal goes and gets something. If you do not point out a specific item, the animal fetches a random object.
ABILITY:Animal Trick|TYPE:NORMAL|CATEGORY:Special Ability|KEY:Animal Trick ~ Heel|TYPE:AnimalTrick|DESC:The animal follows you closely, even to places where it normally wouldn't go.
ABILITY:Animal Trick|TYPE:NORMAL|CATEGORY:Special Ability|KEY:Animal Trick ~ Seek|TYPE:AnimalTrick|DESC:The animal moves into an area and looks around for anything that is obviously alive or animate.
